A former governor of Ondo state and senatorial candidate of the Zenith Labour Party for Ondo Central District, Olusegun Mimiko won his polling unit. He polled 232 votes to win the unit. In the presidential election, Atiku Abubakar of the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, defeated Muhammadu Buhari of the All Progressives Congress, APC at the polling unit. Atiku polled 209 votes while Buhari polled 70 votes.  Ondo west, Ward 7, Unit 20. Presidential
